Unicoa Corp said it agreed to a mergerwith its wholly-owned subsidiary, United Insurance Co ofAmerica.    Under the agreement, each outstanding share of Unicoacommon stock will be converted into one share of United commonstock.    The agreement is subject to shareholder and regulatoryapproval. Teledyne Inc &lt;TDY> owns about 98.4 pct of Unicoa'soutstanding shares. A shareholder meeting is expected to beheld in August. Reuter&#3;